\\\\ Arithmetic in Sigi
\\\\ !N pushes a number onto the stack
\\\\ | pops and prints with newline

!1 |                \\\\ print 1
!2 !3 + |           \\\\ print 5 (2+3)
!10 !3 - |          \\\\ print 7 (10-3)
!4 !5 * |           \\\\ print 20 (4*5)
!20 !4 / |           \\\\ print 5 (20/4)
!17 !5 % |           \\\\ print 2 (17 mod 5)
